name: JacobStats
creator: Squagward
description: Adds a display to check a player's stats of Jacob farming events. Type /jacob to get started.
helpMessage:
§7§lHelp Info:
/jacob to open the gui.
Then type in a player's name and press enter.
To exit that screen, press ESC, left arrow, or delete.
You can hover over different lines to get more information!
